Alaska Airlines Authorized Routes
ANNOUNCING NEW
SERVICE TO:
• Spokane, Washington effective April 24 with daily
flights to/from Seattle connecting to other Alaska
Airlines flights to cities in California, Oregon, and
Alaska.
• Chicago, Illinois and Washington, D.C. from An-
chorage, thru Seattle, on the second Alaska Airlines/
American Airlines Interchange effective May 15,
1982.
• Kodiak, Alaska effective May 31 with daily flights
to/from Anchorage, Seattle, Burbank, Ontario.
Call ALASKA AIRLINES or your travel agent when
your travel plans call for one of our new destinations.
